\[\left( \frac{\partial}{\partial t} \right)_r
= \left( \frac{\partial }{\partial t}\right)_{M_r} + \left( \frac{\partial M_r}{\partial t}\right)_r \left( \frac{\partial}{\partial M_r}\right)_t, \quad
