<p>ã“ã“ã«(1.1.14)å¼ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚Œã°</p>

\[\left( \frac{\partial \rho}{\partial t}\right)_{M_r} + 4\pi \rho^2 \left[ \frac{\partial}{\partial M_r} \left\{ r^2 \left(\frac{\partial r}{\partial t}\right)_{M_r}\right\} \right]_t 
